<title>GREECE: MACEDONIA-THRACE BANK OK'D FOR 2-FOR-10 BONUS ISSUE.</title>
<headline>MACEDONIA-THRACE BANK OK'D FOR 2-FOR-10 BONUS ISSUE.</headline>
<dateline>ATHENS 1997-06-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>The repeat shareholders meeting of Macedonia-Thrace Bank approved a two-for-10 bonus issue, the result of a capitalisation of asset revaluation and share premium reserves, the bank said.</p>
<p>The stock will trade ex-bonus June 26, it said. --Angelos Kiosklis, Athens Newsroom +301 3311812-4</p>
